{"tid":1857214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集氣區］比政府睇下市民有幾咁支持醫護聽日罷工","createTime":"2020-02-02T05:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T05:37:27.000Z","uid":342354,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d8b1ad1efc683a6b2fd84d2bad41f35bdecf69","tid":1857214,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"致前線醫護一段話：<br />\n<br />\n你地好勇敢，呢場工業行動保護左大多數香港人既利益，請記住，你地絕對唔係政府口中置病人不顧既自私醫護，香港政府先係呢場行動既始作俑者，罔顧全香港人既健康。<br />\n<br />\n政府唔該唔好強姦民意，我地絕對支持前線醫護罷工，不向強權低頭。請政府立即封關，回應醫護訴求。<br />\n<br />\n特別感謝員工陣線呢幾日不眠不休組織罷工，辛苦你地同一眾醫護。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足快d入黎感謝罷工醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b58d3e9ec9af2a9eb29e22d7a21234d48e4f1c","tid":1857214,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c5b620d3a67760f3f89655c9087b03a886ff70f","tid":1857214,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁都要推"},{"pid":"d913fe56ffd491d347388cff6745f85b2193cbaf","tid":1857214,"uid":29555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}